  <lyrics>[V1]
 Adanamp Evampi» Diosaw uchawayi,
 Huerto Edenaru jan cuna juchani,
 :Jupanacaw jani Diosarojj ist'cánti
 Ucat jiwafiajja takenitac utji. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Diosajj qhitaniwa rnunat Wawaparu,
 Take acapachar juchat khespiyiri.
 :Jakenacajj ucjja janiw amuyquiti,
 Supayaw engafiji jucha lurafiampi. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Juchan jakenacajj, juicio uruquiwa,
 Diosar thakapjjani. ucqhajj jayp'üniwa.
 :Biblian uqham parli, waquisiw isfafia,
 Jichhürpachay, Cristor, iyawsapjjaftáni. (Bis)
 
</lyrics></song>